          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1687534240298-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>macaroni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>macaroni</strong> for 6-7 min or until cooked with a bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>macaroni</strong> and set aside until later, reserving 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[195ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>sweetcorn cobette[s]</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and put the tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until charred and crispy</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
