    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the macaroni is cooking, peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>grated cheese</strong> with your <strong>cornflour</strong> in a bowl and mix until the cheese is fully coated</p>",
