    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cooked macaroni </strong>to the <strong>cheese sauce</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>mac 'n' cheese mixture</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>mac 'n' cheese mixture</strong> to the reserved dish and top with the <strong>shredded BBQ pulled pork</strong></p><p>Return the dish to the oven for 5-6 min or until golden and bubbling – this is your <strong>BBQ pulled pork mac 'n' cheese</strong></p>",
