    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mac 'n' cheese is in the oven, wash your <strong>baby leaf salad </strong>then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine the <strong>sliced shallot</strong>, <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> in a large bowl with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>mustard dressing</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>baby leaf salad </strong>to the <strong>mustard dressing </strong>and toss – this is your <strong>mustard salad</strong></p>",
